ts that they are rather faint, with M_r<-19.5. (ABRIDGED)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2007 17:40:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Mar 2008 01:10:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
