ts of the X-ray galaxy clusters compared to those derived from\nthe 158 deg^2 ROSAT PSPC survey. Treating sigma_8 as a free parameter, we find\na best-fit value of sigma_8=0.80+/- 0.02.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2007 20:32:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
